description: Redevelopment of existing public house, shop units, showroom/garage & petrol station by the erection of a part 4, part 5 storey building plus basement & sub-basement to provide a gym (Class D2) at part basement & part ground floor, 5 ground floor commercial units (Class A1, A2 or A3 use), 22 affordable residential units at 1st-3rd floors & 50 private residential units at 1st-4th floor levels, plus 82 ancillary parking spaces (outline application).
